      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, really? That sounds super scary. I thought these were just the usual side effects people talk about when starting lithium. Are you sure it's an emergency? I don't really have insurance right now so the ER would be a huge problem for me. Can't I just drink a ton of water and wait a day or two to see if the shakes go away?",
